Tamagotchi kofi commissions for @anextremelysadmeme & @jelliejem 💕 Thank you so much for the Kofis 😊 

 Character Bios if you’re interested: 

 1. A little chemical/potion Tamagotchi who’s easy to care for so long as you always check on their health! ⚗️✨

 2. A summer time Tamagotchi that’s  easy to care as long as you don’t give in to their sweet tooth! If you do you’ll end up with a sluggish orange cream Scream! 🍊 ✨
